gw.bc.invoice

Interface ReturnPremiumSchemeIdentificationPredicate

  • All Superinterfaces:
    LinkedImplementation<ReturnPremiumHandlingCondition>, com.google.common.base.Predicate<java.lang.Iterable<InvoiceItem>>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    OtherReturnPremiumHandlingCondition

    public interface ReturnPremiumSchemeIdentificationPredicate
extends com.google.common.base.Predicate<java.lang.Iterable<InvoiceItem>>, LinkedImplementation<ReturnPremiumHandlingCondition>
    A Return Premium Handling Scheme Identification Predicate interface. Implementing this creates a predicate associated with a ReturnPremiumHandlingCondition type-key that can identify a ReturnPremiumHandlingScheme in a return premium plan that should apply for the input InvoiceItems.
